  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FinTech支付网关设计一个状态流转图。核心场景是：系统启动后先进入INIT初始状态，然后判断is_system_ready条件，就绪后就进入STOPPED暂停态，等待后续触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "INIT",
        "STOPPED",
        "is_system_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，INIT是起点。那STOPPED之后有哪些去向？是单向流转还是可以回退？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "STOPPED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "STOPPED有两个分支：一是如果FinTech_AuthVault那边再次触发is_system_ready为True，就回到INIT重新初始化；二是如果FinTech_FraudDetection检测到射出条件成立，就进入TO_MAX状态，开始额度提升流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOPPED",
        "INIT",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "TO_MAX"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以TO_MAX是额度提升的中间态。那TO_MAX之后怎么收尾？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TO_MAX"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "TO_MAX达到上限后，当ejection_maxlim_on为True时，进入RETURN_TO_MIN状态，开始回退。然后RETURN_TO_MIN检测到ejection_minlim_on为True时，回到STOPPED，完成一个完整循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TO_MAX",
        "RETURN_TO_MIN",
        "STOPPED",
        "ejection_maxlim_on",
        "ejection_minlim_on"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，从FinTech_PaymentGateway指向INIT作为起点，各状态流转关系都按你说的连上了。STOPPED到INIT的触发条件标注了FinTech_AuthVault来源，STOPPED到TO_MAX标注了FinTech_FraudDetection的射出条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "INIT",
        "STOPPED",
        "TO_MAX",
        "RETURN_TO_MIN",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，RETURN_TO_MIN回到STOPPED那条线，条件应该是ejection_minlim_on==True，不是is_system_ready。刚才可能口误了，这个条件对应的是最小限位开关信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RETURN_TO_MIN",
